(--- Setup and Safety Codes ---)
G21          (Set units to Millimeters)
G90          (Set to Absolute Distance Mode)
G17          (Select the X-Y plane)
G40          (Cancel tool radius compensation)
G49          (Cancel tool length offset)

(--- Starting the Test Square ---)
(Ensure we start at the origin at a controlled feedrate)
G0 X0 Y0 Z0   (Rapid move to the origin)
G1 F300     (Set linear interpolation movement speed to 300 mm/min)

(1. Move from origin to X 50)
G1 X50 Y0

(2. From X 50, Y 0, move to Y 50)
G1 X50 Y50

(3. From X 50, Y 50, move back to X 0, Y 50)
G1 X0 Y50

(4. From X 0, Y 50, move back to X 0, Y 0)
G1 X0 Y0

(--- Program End ---)
M2           (End of program)
